        <updateDate>2018-02-12T20:58:07Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Cooling-Off Period Elimination Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill makes a state or local law enforcement agency ineligible to receive federal funds under a Department of Justice law enforcement grant program if it has in effect a cooling-off period. A cooling-off period is a period of time following an officer-involved shooting during which investigators are prohibited from communicating with an officer involved in the shooting. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
