      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To provide that any State or local law enforcement agency that has in effect a cooling-off period is ineligible to receive Federal funds pursuant to a Department of Justice law enforcement grant program, and for other purposes.</title>
